OL,3,CCarlisle businesses damaged by flash
OL,4,Cflooding
OL,6,FBusinesses in Carlisle city centre say
OL,7,Fflash flooding caused thousands of
OL,8,Fpounds worth of damage.
OL,10,FWhile some of the region escaped the
OL,11,Fheavy thunderstorm downpours on
OL,12,FSaturday afternoon, a number of
OL,13,Ftraders in Carlisle were badly
OL,14,Faffected.
OL,16,FFor around 30 mins there was
OL,17,Ftorrential rain which meant lots of
OL,18,Fpeople ran for cover. Restaurants and
OL,19,Fshops were among those caught out by
OL,20,Fthe rain and had to close early due to
OL,21,Fflooding.
