OL,3,CCarlisle businesses damaged by flash
OL,4,Cflooding
OL,6,FThe owner of one store told ITV Border
OL,7,Fthey had to shut because water was
OL,8,Fcoming through the electrics and the
OL,9,Fdoor. Businesses in the Lanes Shopping
OL,10,FCentre were particularly affected:
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
